{
  "stem": "16442.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 311.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this is how [SIGHS] I left Auschwitz-Birkenau and arrived to Bergen-Belsen, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another chapter in my life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was beginning of January, obviously.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, we got out of the wagons-- when they let us out, they took us in to barracks also.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there were no beds, nothing at all, only straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This Wehrmacht soldier hand me his blanket when I left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He must have been 1% better than the others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I was very fortunate to have a blanket because nobody had a blanket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We was lying in-- on the straw, nothing on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And under this blanket, we had, maybe, 10 girls, or as many as we could get under.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we didn't know what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Food we didn't get.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had absolutely no food the first few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "People were starving and freezing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We would go outside and try to find a little grass or, or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But, of course, in January, it's very hard to find-- not even grass you could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And every day, the SS would come in every morning and pick some of the girls out to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were making beds, you know, put pieces of board together and all sorts-- and clean up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was nobody in the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were the first ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Later, we found out that they took the transport out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And of course, we were so weak and hungry and cold that really, we didn't want to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So every morning early, we got up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we ran to the bathrooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You know, that barrack, that long barrack which was called the bathroom, that's where we ran to hide.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
